title: Mens Health UK redesign fonts?
content:
Hi all

The UK version of Men's Health magazine has had a recent redesign (so has the US and IMO much more successful see here:  
 [http://www.spd.org/2013/05/inside-the-mens-health-redesig.php#&panel1-16](http://web.archive.org/web/20150416055557/http:/www.spd.org/2013/05/inside-the-mens-health-redesig.php#&panel1-16 "http://www.spd.org/2013/05/inside-the-mens-health-redesig.php#&panel1-16")

In any case I'm interested in some of the (rounded) headline fonts used in the UK edition - think it could be Stag Rounded can anyone confirm? and indeed suggest what the other fonts are?

[http://www.menshealth.co.uk/latest-issue-mens-health](http://web.archive.org/web/20150416055557/http:/www.menshealth.co.uk/latest-issue-mens-health "http://www.menshealth.co.uk/latest-issue-mens-health")
